    "# Boolean indexing\n",
    "\n",
    " * The Boolean array must be of the same length as the array axis it’s indexing\n",
    " *  data[names == \"Bob\"]\n",
    " * The Python keywords and and or do not work with Boolean arrays.\n",
    "    Use & (and) and | (or) instead."
